Dia harus menerimanya.

530
00:39:34,020 --> 00:39:36,815
Petugas Hwang, tapi aku senior mereka.

531
00:39:36,982 --> 00:39:39,276
Hei, walau benar,
Juru Tulis Goo berusia 26 tahun,

532
00:39:39,359 --> 00:39:41,486
usiamu 19 tahun.
Mana bisa mengumpat padanya?

533
00:39:42,153 --> 00:39:45,282
Kau tak tahu tetua lebih didahulukan?
Tetua didahulukan.

534
00:39:48,326 --> 00:39:49,411
Hei!

535
00:39:50,495 --> 00:39:52,163
Matilah kalian semua.

536
00:39:52,247 --> 00:39:55,000
Kenapa petugas senior peringkat sembilan
dan juru tulis di sini?

537
00:39:55,458 --> 00:39:58,461
Haruskah aku yang melakukan
tugas sejarawan kedua?

538
00:39:58,587 --> 00:40:00,005
Butuh bantuan kami?

539
00:40:00,881 --> 00:40:01,882
Tak perlu.

540
00:40:02,841 --> 00:40:03,925
Kalian berempat.

541
00:40:05,010 --> 00:40:06,928
Sedang apa? Ikut aku.

542
00:41:05,946 --> 00:41:06,821
Apa-apaan ini...

543
00:41:08,114 --> 00:41:10,575
Beraninya wanita masuk kemari?

544
00:41:10,825 --> 00:41:12,118
Keluar!

545
00:41:15,664 --> 00:41:16,539
Ini tempat duduk

546
00:41:17,707 --> 00:41:18,625
para sejarawan.

547
00:41:18,708 --> 00:41:22,796
Petugas Min, kau izinkan kami
ikut rapat kerajaan?

548
00:41:24,297 --> 00:41:25,674
Duduk di posisi kalian.

549
00:41:36,893 --> 00:41:38,019
Petugas Min.

550
00:41:38,395 --> 00:41:40,355
Kau pikir kau sedang apa?

551
00:41:40,939 --> 00:41:42,357
Wanita tak diizinkan kemari.

552
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:44,693
Beraninya kau menodai istana?

553
00:41:45,944 --> 00:41:48,154
Kau sungguh tak sopan.

554
00:41:48,530 --> 00:41:50,365
Beraninya mengabaikan aku?

555
00:41:50,699 --> 00:41:51,950
Sudah cukup.

556
00:42:03,336 --> 00:42:04,879
- Astaga.
- Ini keterlaluan.

557
00:42:08,508 --> 00:42:09,384
Astaga.

558
00:42:13,972 --> 00:42:15,306
- Astaga.
