559
00:42:15,890 --> 00:42:17,642
- Ada apa?
- Ini absurd.

560
00:42:17,726 --> 00:42:20,687
Yang Mulia Pangeran telah tiba.

561
00:42:49,758 --> 00:42:51,051
Kenapa hanya kalian?

562
00:42:51,259 --> 00:42:55,013
